This is the package for ArctineOS' configuration.

The checksum verification does not run, so you need to skip it for now. Run the command like this:

makepkg -sr --skipchecksums

Make sure you are in the same directory as this one when running makepkg

This depends on the parent directory, the Git repository ArctineLabs/OS, do not move it outside of it, it will not work.

To install, run:
pacman -U (insert package name).tar.zst
